title: MC Paul Barman
description:
What can I say about a Jewish hip-hop artist?

MC Paul Barman combines the best of humor and intelligence with the help of MF Doom to create some of the best hip-hop music I&#039;ve ever heard. 

If you haven&#039;t heard him, and enjoy either Hip-Hop or Humorous music (or both) check this out, then go support him at www.Mcpaulbarman.com

Paul B needs to know that there are fans out there who would love to hear more of his music.
